task.summary: Default task
*Renamed to Android Kit *Set the project to use the Gradle wrapper
Added queue() for serial execution of HTTPRequests
Added blur() to BitmapUtils
Optimized the timing of onPostExecute call
Added HTTPRequestBodyProvider for just-in-time building of request bodies which would be useful for queued requests with dependencies
*Implemented a manual queue for better control *Fixed missing onPostExecute *Fixed logging of SSL verification flag
Added getRequestQueue() and clearRequestQueue()
Added empty queue check
*Added queueFirst() and dequeue() *executeAsync(), queue(), queueFirst() and dequeue() now returns the HTTPRequest object
Ensured that executeFromQueueIfFree() will still be called even on error scenarios
Added missing onRequestTerminated()
Refactored and added several methods to AppUtils and SystemUtils
Added launch URL
Changed launchURL to launchURI (more appropriate)
Added BitmapLoader for even simpler loading and displaying of Bitmaps
targetWidth and targetHeight are now optional for Bitmap decoding methods and in BitmapResponseListener
Added a new method and some documentation in BitmapLoader
*Fixed SecureDataFile not loading properly *Added some checks in SecureData when loading encrypted data *Added logging in SecureDataFile *Some refactoring
Added ability to set a MockResponse for HTTPRequests
Added documentation on MockResponse
